params._carToken: The token used to purchase cars

getCarCount(address).details: Returns the amount of cars a car owner has.

getCarFactory().details: Gets the address of the Car factory

isExistingCustomer(address).details: Checks if a customer has previously purchased a car

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

purchaseCar(string,string,string).details: Enables a user to purchase a car

params._color: The color of the car to be purchased
params._model: The model of the car to be purchased
params._plateNumber: The plateNumber of the car to be purchased

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._factory: The address of the car factory.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

constructor.notice: Sets the car token during deployment.

setCarFactory(address).notice: Sets the car factory after deployment.
